title: Trombonists to converge for sixth Trombone Summit (University of Wisconsin - Eau Claire)
text: ( Source : University of Wisconsin - Eau Claire ) More than 100 trombone players will participate Oct. 18 in the sixth Upper Midwest Trombone Summit in the Haas Fine Arts Center at UW-Eau Claire . The summit sessions and final concert are free
